    "Such a language can minimize ambiguities and ensure clear instructions, resulting in more reliable and accurate outputs.",
    "Current State.",
    "Multiple prompting frameworks are released to facilitate the usage of LLMs.",
    "For example, DSPy [67] and Vieira [79] enable fully automated generation of prompts.",
    "AutoGen [145] and LangChain [97] support retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) [38] and agent-based workflows."
